{"tid":1631061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登明顯有班鼓吹無差別裝修既ac帶緊風向","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:43.000Z","uid":138609,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ed4ce508c6a08c585b649a35187996f07b4367","tid":1631061,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"首先 裝修唔反對 亦唔會割蓆<br />\n但係明明有左黑紅藍黃既共識<br />\n仲有班人鼓吹緊無差別裝修<br />\n特別係格離石硤尾餐廳下面既回覆<br />\n一黎未FC 二黎即使係藍絲<br />\n罷食 最多裝飾已經夠 但睇評論<br />\n個個一味叫人去裝修裝修裝修<br />\n明顯有組織帶緊風向<br />\n港共想借滲透連登瓦解呢場革命<br />\n我信前線手足有腦知道自己做緊乜<br />\n而且無勇武根本唔會行到呢一步<br />\n和理非們請繼續做勇武後盾<br />\n團結不分化不篤灰不割蓆<br />\n特別唔好屌手足老母<br />\n自己人即使諗法唔同唔洗屌人or發爛渣既<br />\n呢家打緊仗 冷靜理智行下一步先唔會行錯<br />\n我地得一次機會 唔會有第二次<br />\n天佑香港 天佑香港人"},{"pid":"8a7e527111460049daca68764d3cbea59385c82e","tid":1631061,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8859e331b7daf021fedcb6098dde655d1ac91862","tid":1631061,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb992ea0bf982703efc1a07e8b2dc03daf07bb95","tid":1631061,"uid":104648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:37:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ae0895471c91fd544752a57631e69b2c9772f305","tid":1631061,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b